## Token Security Checklist 

### Detect Unauthorized Token Minting
Ensure tokens cannot be created without proper authorization through direct minting functions.

```solidity
// Vulnerable: Anyone can mint tokens
function mint(address to, uint256 amount) external {
    _totalSupply += amount;
    _balances[to] += amount;
}

// Vulnerable: Hidden minting through internal functions
function reward(address user) external {
    _mint(user, 1000 * 10**18); // no access control
}
```

**Invariant:** Add proper access control (onlyOwner, onlyMinter) to all minting functions.
